Package tachyon.client

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RemoteBlockReader
    The interface to read remote block from data server.
    RemoteBlockWriter
    The interface to write a remote block to the data server.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BlockInStream
    BlockInStream interface implementation of TachyonFile.
    BlockOutStream
    BlockOutStream interface for writing data to a block.
    ClientConstants
    Constants on server side
    EmptyBlockInStream
    EmptyBlockInStream is an InStream that can not read anything.
    FileInStream
    FileInStream implementation of TachyonFile.
    FileOutStream
    FileOutStream implementation of TachyonFile.
    InStream
    InStream is the base class of input stream for TachyonFile streaming input.
    LocalBlockInStream
    BlockInStream for local block.
    LocalBlockOutStream
    This implementation of BlockOutStream writes a single block to the local file system.
    OutStream
    OutStream is the base class of output stream for TachyonFile streaming output.
    RemoteBlockInStream
    BlockInStream for remote block.
    RemoteBlockOutStream
    This implementation of BlockOutStream writes a single block to a remote worker.
    RemoteBlockReader.Factory  
    RemoteBlockWriter.Factory  
    TachyonByteBuffer
    TachyonByteBuffer is a wrapper on Java ByteBuffer plus some information needed by Tachyon.
    TachyonFile
    Tachyon File.
    TachyonFS
    Client API to use Tachyon as a file system.
    UfsUtils
    Utilities related to under filesystem
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ReadType
    Different read types for a TachyonFile.
    WriteType
    Different write types for a TachyonFile.
